          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>The unique <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00KF.xml" title="function" addr="jms-00KF" type="local">function</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[!_A\colon  A\to  {\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00M8.xml" title="surjection" addr="jms-00M8" type="local">surjective</fr:link> if and only if <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A \not =\varnothing ]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
 
   
